        <item>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b style=""></b><b style="">Restoring Education And Learning Act of 2016 or the REAL Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill amends title IV (Student Assistance) of the Higher Education Act of 1965 to eliminate the provision that prohibits Pell Grant eligibility for individuals incarcerated in a federal or state penal institution and for sex offenders subject to civil commitment following incarceration. </p> <p>This amendment takes effect in academic year 2016-2017. </p>]]></text>
